WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.300 --> 00:00:03.366
Oops, it's getting late.

2
00:00:03.366 --> 00:00:05.000
Grandma should go back too

3
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.300
You and Wanqing are so good

4
00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:09.433
Grandma, don't worry.

5
00:00:09.600 --> 00:00:11.400
Well, I'm leaving, grandma, I'll take you there.

6
00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:14.500
Oh, no, no, no, come to the housekeeper, grandma, slow down.

7
00:00:14.566 --> 00:00:16.066
Oh good

8
00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:22.566
Hey, Manager Liu, okay.

9
00:00:22.766 --> 00:00:24.200
Okay, I'll be right there.

10
00:00:25.133 --> 00:00:26.000
What's up

11
00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:28.733
The company called, and Manager Liu said to talk to me about something.

12
00:00:28.733 --> 00:00:30.066
Let me go now

13
00:00:30.533 --> 00:00:31.500
Or you can step back

14
00:00:31.666 --> 00:00:33.700
Then bring me a cup of milk tea on the way.

15
00:00:33.933 --> 00:00:37.800
Forget love, thank you, what do we have?

16
00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:42.566
Thank you for everything I wanted to say to my grandmother

17
00:00:42.566 --> 00:00:43.400
It's all said

18
00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:46.300
In fact, love is very simple, don't think so much

19
00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:50.133
Well, I'll go to the company first. Hmm.

20
00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:52.866
Remember to bring me milk tea, okay.

21
00:00:58.700 --> 00:01:01.466
Hey, what are you doing?

22
